
<h1>About Us</h1>
<p>
  HYGWIT is a project to streamline and strengthen HR operations in Gulf businesses, covering every aspect of employee management in a single integrated package.
</p>
  
<p>In particular, we aim to:
  <ul>
    <li>Eliminate paperwork and redundant administrative processes.</li>
    <li>Put much more focus on bottom-line achievement.</li>
    <li>Use mobile technology to give management and staff relevant, up-to-the-moment information.</li>
    <li>Reduce the cost of HR software</li>
  </ul>
</p>
    
<p>Find out more about us and our objectives at the <a href="http://www.hroomph.com" target="_blank">HROomph website</a>. 
</p>

